8	Producer/tech-kickoff-meetings	f1589983b27654191e5097521e4f2e3b02a3f4ad	Tech Kickoff Meetings		f	t			deleted	6	<p>A <strong>Tech Kickoff Meeting</strong> should be held <u>once a job is awarded</u>. The purpose of this meeting is:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Review technical workflow of the project</li>\n  <li>Determine frame rate, size and naming</li>\n  <li>Discuss the workflow between departments</li>\n  <li>Confirm server/folder organization</li>\n  <li>Determine who is entering notes into the tracker (Producer or PC)</li>\n  <li>Notify Sara in Ops with any in-studio resource needs (IE workstations + software and/or licenses)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Oftentimes, follow up Tech Meetings are needed throughout production, usually at each major stage. Examples include (but are not limited to):</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Stop Motion/Live - Pre Shoot Creative Kick-Off</li>\n  <li>Stop Motion/Live - VFX/Post Kick-Off</li>\n  <li>2D/Cel - 2D Prep Kick-Off</li>\n  <li>2D/Cel - 2D Animator Kick-Off</li>\n  <li>2D-Cel - AE Comp Kick-Off</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br>&nbsp;</p>\n	html	2021-07-14T18:31:13.756Z	ckeditor	en	1	2021-07-14T17:24:21.954Z	{}
