 prerenders, stock, and animatics.</span></p><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 30pt; padding-left: 0; text-indent: 0;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 30pt; padding-left: 0; text-indent: 0;"><span style="font-family: 'Lato'; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong>05_Collected_Project_Files </strong></span></p><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 30pt; padding-left: 0; text-indent: 0;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline;">Collected projects from other artists that you are bringing into your comp. </span></p><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 30pt; padding-left: 0; text-indent: 0;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline;">Example:</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline;"> You’re using end tags from a spot made last year. Collect the end tags here and import into your AEP.</span></p><div id="h.yehps4sanewc" class="GV3q8e aP9Z7e"></div><h3 id="h.yehps4sanewc" dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q OmQG5e" style="line-height: 1.38;" tabindex="-1"><div jscontroller="Ae65rd" jsaction="touchstart:UrsOsc; click:KjsqPd; focusout:QZoaZ; mouseover:y0pDld; mouseout:dq0hvd;fv1Rjc:jbFSOd;CrfLRd:SzACGe;" class="CjVfdc"><div class="PPhIP rviiZ" jsname="haAclf"><div role="presentation" class="U26fgb mUbCce fKz7Od LRAOtb Znu9nd M9Bg4d" jscontroller="mxS5xe" jsaction="click:cOuCgd; mousedown:UX7yZ; mouseup:lbsD7e; mouseenter:tfO1Yc; mouseleave:JywGue; focus:AHmuwe; blur:O22p3e; contextmenu:mg9Pef;" jsshadow="" aria-describedby="h.yehps4sanewc" aria-label="Copy heading link" aria-disabled="false" data-tooltip="Copy heading link" aria-hidden="true" data-tooltip-position="top" data-tooltip-vertical-offset="12" data-tooltip-horizontal-offset="0"><a class="FKF6mc TpQm9d" href="#h.yehps4sanewc" aria-label="Copy heading link" jsname="hiK3ld" role="button" aria-describedby="h.yehps4sanewc"><div class="VTBa7b MbhUzd" jsname="ksKsZd"></div><span jsslot="" class="xjKiLb"><span class="Ce1Y1c" style="top: -11px"><svg class="OUGEr QdAdhf" width="22px" height="22px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" focusable="false"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"></path></svg></span></span></a></div></div>03_ae_output</div></h3><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 15pt; padding-left: 0; text-indent: 0;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline;">This is where your renders will go within a dated folder.*  This directory is also for any reference videos/images you need to kick out of AE for 2D.   </span></p><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 15pt; padding-left: 0; text-indent: 0;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><em>*Once you QC your render, copy dailies for director review into dailies in the project root, and postings for client should go into post in the project root.*</em></span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="h.4d5e03e885f40463_50" class="yaqOZd" style=""><div class="IFuOkc"></div><div class="mYVXT"><div class="LS81yb VICjCf" tabindex="-1"><div class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd purZT-AhqUyc-II5mzb pSzOP-AhqUyc-qWD73c JNdkSc"><div class="JNdkSc-SmKAyb"><div class="" jscontroller="sGwD4d" jsaction="zXBUYb:zTPCnb;zQF9Uc:Qxe3nd;" jsname="F57UId"><div class="oKdM2c Kzv0Me"><div id="h.4d5e03e885f40463_47" class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd jXK9ad D2fZ2 OjCsFc wHaque GNzUNc"><div class="jXK9ad-SmKAyb"><div class="tyJCtd mGzaTb baZpAe"><div id="h.pn056n6aiu5x" class="CobnVe aP9Z7e"></div><h2 id="h.pn056n6aiu5x" dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q JYVBee" tabi