: baseline;">It will open up this dialogue</span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline;">:</span></p></div></div></div></div><div class="oKdM2c"><div id="h.56e95cbdacedae36_64" class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-qWD73c jXK9ad D2fZ2 wHaque"><div class="jXK9ad-SmKAyb"><div class="tyJCtd baZpAe"><div class="t3iYD"><img src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/PcjRFz6GrzQWolf76EjdY7R7ds1p-o3QKJmlfenlEuQ3t2qkBW_PpdZ63xqFBs7Q6-B0NXqA9OHQz0NWmFCFy7Q3YztDG3Tg6SMJUWPnr7EjIMlEHnrfyGSkJJOXOTicfA=w1280" class="CENy8b" role="img"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-qWD73c JNdkSc L6cTce-purZT L6cTce-pSzOP"><div class="JNdkSc-SmKAyb"><div class="" jscontroller="sGwD4d" jsaction="zXBUYb:zTPCnb;zQF9Uc:Qxe3nd;" jsname="F57UId"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="h.4d5e03e885f40463_3" class="yaqOZd" style=""><div class="IFuOkc"></div><div class="mYVXT"><div class="LS81yb VICjCf" tabindex="-1"><div class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd purZT-AhqUyc-II5mzb pSzOP-AhqUyc-qWD73c JNdkSc"><div class="JNdkSc-SmKAyb"><div class="" jscontroller="sGwD4d" jsaction="zXBUYb:zTPCnb;zQF9Uc:Qxe3nd;" jsname="F57UId"><div class="oKdM2c Kzv0Me"><div id="h.4d5e03e885f40463_0" class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd jXK9ad D2fZ2 OjCsFc wHaque GNzUNc"><div class="jXK9ad-SmKAyb"><div class="tyJCtd mGzaTb baZpAe"><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q" style="background-color: transparent; border-bottom: none; border-left: none; border-right: none; border-top: none; line-height: 1.656; margin-bottom: 0; margin-left: 15pt; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-top: 0; text-align: left; text-indent: 0;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline;">3.</span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Lato'; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong> </strong></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Lato'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; text-decoration: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong>COPY/PASTE THIS TEXT</strong></span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; text-decoration: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"> into your “Template:” text field:</span></p><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q" style="background-color: transparent; border-bottom: none; border-left: none; border-right: none; border-top: none; line-height: 1.656; margin-bottom: 0; margin-left: 15pt; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-top: 0; text-align: left; text-indent: 0;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Lato'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; text-decoration: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong>[compName]_[dateYear][dateMonth][dateDay]_v01.[fileExtension]</strong></span></p><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q" style="background-color: transparent; border-bottom: none; border-left: none; border-right: none; border-top: none; line-height: 1.656; margin-bottom: 0; margin-left: 15pt; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-top: 0; text-align: left; text-indent: 0;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q" style="background-color: transparent; border-bottom: none; border-left: none; border-right: none; border-top: none; line-height: 1.656; margin-bottom: 0; margin-left: 15pt; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-top: 0; text-align: left; text-indent: 0;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline;">4.</span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Lato'; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong> </strong></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Lato'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; text-decoration: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong>Press the new preset button </strong></span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; text-decoration: normal; vertical-align: baseline;">(looks like a layer button). </span></p><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q" style="margin-left: 15pt; padding-left: 0; text-indent: 0;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline;">5. </span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; text-decoration: normal; vertical-align: baseline;">Name your Preset IE: </span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Lato'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; text-decoration: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong>YearMonthDay_v01, </strong></span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline;">click OK</span></p><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q" style="margin-left: 15pt; padding-left: 0; text-indent: 0;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline;">6. Then select “Default” back on the main menu. Every time you add a new file to your queue, it will automatically be given this naming convention.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="h.4d5e03e885f40463_10" class="yaqOZd" style=""><div class="IFuOkc"></div><div class="mYVXT"><div class="LS81yb VICjCf" tabindex="-1"><div class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-qWD73c purZT-AhqUyc-II5mzb pSzOP-AhqUyc-qWD73c JNdkSc"><div class="JNdkSc-SmKAyb"><div class="" jscontroller="sGwD4d" jsaction="zXBUYb:zTPCnb;zQF9Uc:Qxe3nd;" jsname="F57UId"><div class="oKdM2c Kzv0Me"><div id="h.4d5e03e885f40463_28" class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-qWD73c jXK9ad D2fZ2 OjCsFc wHaque"><div class="jXK9ad-SmKAyb"><div class="tyJCtd baZpAe"><div class="t3iYD"><img src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/wIo9aWTYN2AJ4njSGFcfmKQcXpx8WT6fwZs-ab7UFofabNTHYybWZtanzp-80RI4uXOmpvCS255UjGNj65rNvh3lg5WKQ_o-YebrLP4UKO2Noquvz97LLZmbBMHfzuq2dA=w1280" class="CENy8b" role="img"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-qWD73c purZT-AhqUyc-II5mzb pSzOP-AhqUyc-qWD73c JNdkSc"><div class="JNdkSc-SmKAyb"><div class="" jscontroller="sGwD4d" jsaction="zXBUYb:zTPCnb;zQF9Uc: