19	producer/breakdown-meetings	c3d0aaf11fff8d8fc7c46a243783bfbf067ac3bb	Breakdown Meetings		f	t	\N			<p>A <strong>Breakdown Meeting</strong> should be held once there is a locked Animatic/ Pre-vis or Storyboard. The purpose of this meeting is:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To review and build upon the plan discussed in the Tech Kickoff Meeting</li>\n  <li>To confirm a plan of action for production, shot-by-shot, and affirm techniqes to be used for all aspects of shots</li>\n  <li>To create an asset list for designs or other assets</li>\n  <li>To designate who will handle which parts of production, shot-by-shot and who will create assets</li>\n  <li>To "cast" characters for all shots</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br>&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>A <strong>Breakdown Meeting</strong> should be held once there is a locked Animatic/ Pre-vis or Storyboard. The purpose of this meeting is:</p><div>\n</div><p>&nbsp;</p><div>\n</div><ul>\n  <li>To review and build upon the plan discussed in the Tech Kickoff Meeting</li>\n  <li>To confirm a plan of action for production, shot-by-shot, and affirm techniqes to be used for all aspects of shots</li>\n  <li>To create an asset list for designs or other assets</li>\n  <li>To designate who will handle which parts of production, shot-by-shot and who will create assets</li>\n  <li>To "cast" characters for all shots</li>\n</ul><div>\n</div><p><br>&nbsp;</p><div>\n</div>	[]	html	2021-07-14T18:30:08.299Z	2021-07-14T18:30:10.848Z	ckeditor	en	3	3	{"js":"","css":""}
20	producer/tech-kickoff-meetings	9dea7238ea7e94b6fc1b621efb2c14e888050e28	Tech Kickoff Meetings		f	t	\N			<p>A <strong>Tech Kickoff Meeting</strong> should be held <u>once a job is awarded</u>. The purpose of this meeting is:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Review technical workflow of the project</li>\n  <li>Determine frame rate, size and naming</li>\n  <li>Discuss the workflow between departments</li>\n  <li>Confirm server/folder organization</li>\n  <li>Determine who is entering notes into the tracker (Producer or PC)</li>\n  <li>Notify Sara in Ops with any in-studio resource needs (IE workstations + software and/or licenses)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Oftentimes, follow up Tech Meetings are needed throughout production, usually at each major stage. Examples include (but are not limited to):</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Stop Motion/Live - Pre Shoot Creative Kick-Off</li>\n  <li>Stop Motion/Live - VFX/Post Kick-Off</li>\n  <li>2D/Cel - 2D Prep Kick-Off</li>\n  <li>2D/Cel - 2D Animator Kick-Off</li>\n  <li>2D-Cel - AE Comp Kick-Off</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br>&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>A <strong>Tech Kickoff Meeting</strong> should be held <u>once a job is awarded</u>. The purpose of this meeting is:</p><div>\n</div><p>&nbsp;</p><div>\n</div><ul>\n  <li>Review technical workflow of the project</li>\n  <li>Determine frame rate, size and naming</li>\n  <li>Discuss the workflow between departments</li>\n  <li>Confirm server/folder organization</li>\n  <li>Determine who is entering notes into the tracker (Producer or PC)</li>\n  <li>Notify Sara in Ops with any in-studio resource needs (IE workstations + software and/or licenses)</li>\n</ul><div>\n</div><p>&nbsp;</p><div>\n</div><p>Oftentimes, follow up Tech Meetings are needed throughout production, usually at each major stage. Examples include (but are not limited to):</p><div>\n</div><ul>\n  <li>Stop Motion/Live - Pre Shoot Creative Kick-Off</li>\n  <li>Stop Motion/Live - VFX/Post Kick-Off</li>\n  <li>2D/Cel - 2D Prep Kick-Off</li>\n  <li>2D/Cel - 2D Animator Kick-Off</li>\n  <li>2D-Cel - AE Comp Kick-Off</li>\n</ul><div>\n</div><p><br>&nbsp;</p><div>\n</div>	[]	html	2021-07-14T18:30:38.594Z	2021-07-14T18:30:41.119Z	ckeditor	en	3	3	{"js":"","css":""}
